author: Tanya Li For Daily Mail Australia
title: Damaged Apple screens from Australia Post received twice | Daily Mail Online
text: Is this what we get for our $5.6 million a year? Computer repair man receives TWO MacBooks with cracked screens in the mail from Australia Post - after revelations the company's boss is world's best paid Computer repairer Paul, 57, ordered two of the same screens in November 2016 The man from Maryborough, Victoria ordered the first but it was damaged He then ordered a new one on the same day, but it was also broken He said it was cracked despite being bubble wrapped with foam and cardboard Paul claims Australia Post would've had to be quite rough to break the screens Published: 02:59 GMT, 9 February 2017 | Updated: 04:38 GMT, 10 February 2017 151 shares
